		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />@artakserkso
<br />the nes-004e controllers should work fine, don't know about the power supply though as all nes stuff that ends with e that i've seen are some kind of bastards and doesn't want to be compatible with anything else (besides the controller)... in the case of the wall wart, it's the inner diameter thats different... which color is the power supply socket on the nes unit?
<br />
<br />if blue =&gt; will not work, been there, done that <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" />
<br />if black =&gt; will most likely work (a pal nes wall wart worked on a ntsc unit i had)
